brother got in with uncle's ratio card.

6
00:02:10,246 --> 00:02:13,233
Come on!

7
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:19,222
Come on, boys!
All together, go!

8
00:02:19,749 --> 00:02:22,212
One... One, two, three!
Go!

9
00:02:23,941 --> 00:02:25,769
I had you all!

10
00:02:25,817 --> 00:02:28,088
How happy we were.

11
00:02:28,133 --> 00:02:32,119
Happy to be twenty,
happy to enjoy those summer nights,

12
00:02:32,166 --> 00:02:34,721
and above all,
happy to be together.

13
00:02:34,761 --> 00:02:38,429
