14
00:02:38,474 --> 00:02:41,983
My brother, Giulio, the innocent.

15
00:02:42,028 --> 00:02:45,616
Ettore, the women's idol.

16
00:02:45,661 --> 00:02:48,886
Marcello, last in races,
first in love.

17
00:02:48,935 --> 00:02:52,001
Franco, the craziest, merriest
and happiest of us all.

18
00:02:52,368 --> 00:02:53,719
