19
00:02:53,766 --> 00:02:58,353
Boys, I 'm not sleepy, I wanna have
fun! Roars the lion!

20
00:02:58,397 --> 00:03:02,066
- Where should we go? - The bar at the
station, there's where women are. - Yes.

21
00:03:02,111 --> 00:03:06,062
