64
00:06:34,878 --> 00:06:40,737
"Guido, I'd wish that you, Lapo and I
were bewitched away... "

65
00:06:40,787 --> 00:06:43,250
".. and put in a vessel
that all winds... "

66
00:06:43,302 --> 00:06:46,016
Long live freedom! Ole!

67
00:06:46,057 --> 00:06:49,282
I'm going up!
Up and up!

68
00:06:49,331 --> 00:06:52,761
Hey, guys, I'm flying!

69
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:59,108
Good evening, good...

70
00:06:59,153 --> 00:07:02,423
I don't want to sing anymore!

71
00:07:04,343 --> 00:07:08,488
- You don't want to sing? Hey?
Answer! - No.

72
